---

<section class="mb-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center mb-12">
        <span
            class="text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold mb-2 block"
            >Experiencias Únicas</span
        >
        <h2 class="font-serif text-5xl text-gray-900 leading-tight">
            Vive la <span class="text-secondary">Aventura Peruana</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Ofrecemos experiencias únicas que combinan adrenalina, naturaleza y
            cultura para sacar en cada aventura lo mejor de tí.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"
    >
        <!-- Card 1: Surf & Olas -->
        <div
            class="group relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                <img
                    src="/images/surf.webp"
                    alt="Surf"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    width="600"
                    height="400"
                />
                <div
                    class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-md"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-secondary"
                        >surfing</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Surf & Olas
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Desde principiantes hasta expertos, encuentra las mejores
                    olas en playas como Chicama, la ola izquierda más larga del
                    mundo, y Máncora.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-50 text-primary text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-orange-200"
                        >Clases para todos</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-secondary text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-blue-200"
                        >Alquiler de equipos</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Parapente -->
        <div
            class="group relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                <img
                    src="/images/paragliding.webp"
                    alt="Parapente en Miraflores Lima"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    width="600"
                    height="400"
                />
                <div
                    class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-md"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-sky-500"
                        >paragliding</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Parapente y Tandem
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Vuela sobre la Costa Verde en Lima y disfruta de vistas
                    espectaculares del Océano Pacífico con instructores
                    certificados.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-secondary text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-blue-200"
                        >Adrenalina pura</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-gray-100"
                        >Vistas increíbles</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Transporte Premium -->
        <div
            class="group relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                <img
                    src="/images/transport.webp"
                    alt="Transporte"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    width="600"
                    height="400"
                />
                <div
                    class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-md"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-secondary"
                        >directions_bus</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Transporte Premium
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Viaja cómodo y seguro con nuestro servicio de transporte
                    privado desde Lima a todos los spots más lejanos de la
                    costa.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-secondary text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-blue-200"
                        >Vans privadas</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-secondary text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-blue-200"
                        >Aire acondicionado</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Gastronomía -->
        <div
            class="group relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                <img
                    src="/images/gastronomy.webp"
                    alt="Gastronomía"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    width="600"
                    height="400"
                />
                <div
                    class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-md"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-primary"
                        >restaurant</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Gastronomía
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Deléitate con el mejor ceviche del mundo y la cocina peruana
                    galardonada mundialmente en cada parada de tu viaje.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-50 text-primary text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-orange-200"
                        >Sabores auténticos</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 text-xs font-bold rounded-full border border-gray-100"
                        >Pescado fresco</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
